{"article_id":"pksOcgdVhVsr7pny","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Actor Jussie Smollett was charged on Wednesday with lying to police","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"when he claimed","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"he was attacked and beaten on the streets of Chicago by two masked men","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"shouting racist and homophobic slurs ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"police said on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"as they sought his arrest .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Smollett , a 36-year-old black , openly gay actor on the hip-hop TV drama \" Empire , \" ignited a firestorm on social media","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"by telling police on Jan. 29","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that two apparent supporters of U.S. President Donald Trump struck him ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"put a noose around his neck","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"and poured bleach over him .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"\" Felony criminal charges have been approved by @ CookCountySAO against Jussie Smollett for Disorderly Conduct / Filing a False Police Report .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Detectives will make contact with his legal team","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"to negotiate a reasonable surrender for his arrest , \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"police spokesman Anthony Guglielmi said on Twitter .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The New York Times ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"citing unnamed law enforcement sources ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Smollett had been indicted by an Illinois grand jury","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that found probable cause","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that he had staged the attack .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" Like any other citizen , Mr. Smollett enjoys the presumption of innocence ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"particularly when there has been an investigation like this one","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"where information ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"both true and false , has been repeatedly leaked .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Given these circumstances ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"we intend to conduct a thorough investigation","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and to mount an aggressive defense , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Smollett ' s attorneys , Todd Pugh and Victor Henderson , said in a written statement .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Twentieth Century Fox Television ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"which produces \" Empire , \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"declined comment","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"when told earlier on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that Smollett had been formally named a suspect in the case .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Earlier in the day , the studio said :","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"\" Jussie Smollett continues to be a consummate professional on set","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"as we have previously stated ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he is not being written out of the show . \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Smollett has stood by his account","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"even as police failed to find any evidence of an assault","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and suspicions grew on social media","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that it was a hoax .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Last week , Chicago police questioned two Nigerian brothers","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"recognized from surveillance footage","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"near the scene of the supposed attack ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"but released them two days later , without charge , in light of what investigators said","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"was new evidence .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"TV station CBS Chicago on Wednesday released a videotape","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"it had obtained","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"showing the two brothers","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"buying a red hat and ski masks from a hardware store days before the alleged attack .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Smollett told police","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"his assailants were white ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that one wore a red hat ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and that they shouted something about \" MAGA country \"","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"- an apparent reference to Trump ' s campaign slogan \" Make America Great Again \" -","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"as they struck him to the ground ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"the New York Times has reported .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Chicago police say","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"the charge","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"of filing a false police report","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"carries a maximum sentence of up to three years in prison .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"\" Empire \" has earned multiple Emmy nominations since its 2015 debut .","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"Smollett plays the character Jamal Lyon , a member of the family","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"that is the focus of the show .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":132,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":109,"right":128,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":95,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":87,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":72,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":1,"right":69,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":2,"right":68,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":80,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":76,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":7,"right":75,"rela